### Get data
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolio/report?tickers=AAPL:0.5,MSFT:0.5&riskFreeRate=0.0

### Create
POST http://localhost:5138/portfolios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Test Portfolio",
  "tickerWeights": { "AAPL": 0.5, "MSFT": 0.5 }
}

### 1. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5138/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "test@test.com", "password": "Test123" }

### 2. Login — copy the "token" value from the response
POST http://localhost:5138/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "test@test.com", "password": "Test123" }

### 3. Create a portfolio — paste your token below
POST http://localhost:5138/portfolios
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJodHRwOi8vc2NoZW1hcy54bWxzb2FwLm9yZy93cy8yMDA1LzA1L2lkZW50aXR5L2NsYWltcy9uYW1laWRlbnRpZmllciI6IjExOWRmZWI0LTYzZjYtNGRlZC05MDQ4LTk4ZmI0OTY3YTQwYSIsImh0dHA6Ly9zY2hlbWFzLnhtbHNvYXAub3JnL3dzLzIwMDUvMDUvaWRlbnRpdHkvY2xhaW1zL2VtYWlsYWRkcmVzcyI6InRlc3RAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJleHAiOjE3ODQ4NDU0NTl9.0ZT2q5FZbxvVvcEW3LOuPYiokFH-lVNm7bLorpzJhno

{
  "name": "My First Portfolio",
  "tickerWeights": { "AAPL": 0.5, "MSFT": 0.5 }
}

### 4. List portfolios (should show the one you just created)
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolios
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJodHRwOi8vc2NoZW1hcy54bWxzb2FwLm9yZy93cy8yMDA1LzA1L2lkZW50aXR5L2NsYWltcy9uYW1laWRlbnRpZmllciI6IjExOWRmZWI0LTYzZjYtNGRlZC05MDQ4LTk4ZmI0OTY3YTQwYSIsImh0dHA6Ly9zY2hlbWFzLnhtbHNvYXAub3JnL3dzLzIwMDUvMDUvaWRlbnRpdHkvY2xhaW1zL2VtYWlsYWRkcmVzcyI6InRlc3RAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJleHAiOjE3ODQ4NDU1NDd9.fRFRbzqEELbuVov9dxF-3YYqp-2MRTTXPJLadJlfqSU

### 5. Get portfolio by id — replace 1 with the actual id from step 3's response
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolios/4
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJodHRwOi8vc2NoZW1hcy54bWxzb2FwLm9yZy93cy8yMDA1LzA1L2lkZW50aXR5L2NsYWltcy9uYW1laWRlbnRpZmllciI6IjExOWRmZWI0LTYzZjYtNGRlZC05MDQ4LTk4ZmI0OTY3YTQwYSIsImh0dHA6Ly9zY2hlbWFzLnhtbHNvYXAub3JnL3dzLzIwMDUvMDUvaWRlbnRpdHkvY2xhaW1zL2VtYWlsYWRkcmVzcyI6InRlc3RAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJleHAiOjE3ODQ4NDU0NTl9.0ZT2q5FZbxvVvcEW3LOuPYiokFH-lVNm7bLorpzJhno

### 6. Try without a token — should return 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolios

### 7. Delete it
DELETE http://localhost:5138/portfolios/4
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJodHRwOi8vc2NoZW1hcy54bWxzb2FwLm9yZy93cy8yMDA1LzA1L2lkZW50aXR5L2NsYWltcy9uYW1laWRlbnRpZmllciI6IjExOWRmZWI0LTYzZjYtNGRlZC05MDQ4LTk4ZmI0OTY3YTQwYSIsImh0dHA6Ly9zY2hlbWFzLnhtbHNvYXAub3JnL3dzLzIwMDUvMDUvaWRlbnRpdHkvY2xhaW1zL2VtYWlsYWRkcmVzcyI6InRlc3RAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJleHAiOjE3ODQ4NDU1NDd9.fRFRbzqEELbuVov9dxF-3YYqp-2MRTTXPJLadJlfqSU

